== 名人 ==
著名思想家[[李贽|李贽]]和[[顾准|顾准]]曾在商城居住过。
*[[刘可法|刘可法]]，[[明朝|明朝]][[浙江巡抚|浙江巡抚]]
*[[熊奋渭|熊奋渭]]，明朝浙江巡抚、[[兵部侍郎|兵部侍郎]]，清朝[[刑部右侍郎|刑部右侍郎]]
*[[程国仁|程国仁]]，清嘉庆四年进士，官至[[浙江巡抚|浙江巡抚]]、[[山东巡抚|山东巡抚]]、[[陕西巡抚|陕西巡抚]]、[[贵州巡抚|贵州巡抚]]、[[刑部侍郎|刑部侍郎]]。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-tw | publisher = 中华民国[[中央研究院歷史語言研究所|中央研究院歷史語言研究所]] | title = 程國仁 基本資料 | url = http://npmhost.npm.gov.tw/ttscgi2/ttsquery?0:0:npmauac:TM%3D%B5%7B%B0%EA%A4%AF | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2021-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210816103427/http://npmhost.npm.gov.tw/ttscgi2/ttsquery?0:0:npmauac:TM%3D%B5%7B%B0%EA%A4%AF | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*[[周祖培|周祖培]]，清嘉庆二十四年进士，官至[[兵部尚书|兵部尚书]]、[[吏部尚书|吏部尚书]]、[[户部尚书|户部尚书]]。<ref>{{zh-hant}}《清史稿》卷三九〇·列传一百七十七</ref>
*[[周德荣|周德荣]]，清道光二十七年进士。<ref>{{zh-hant}}《词林辑略》卷六·道光丁未：“周德荣，字少桓，号吉云，河南商城人。”</ref>
*[[洪永安|洪永安]]，清朝著名将领。
*[[林伯襄|林伯襄]]，[[河南大学|河南大学]]前身——河南留学欧美预备学校'''首任校长'''，著名的教育家。

*[[洪学智|洪学智]]，原[[中国人民解放军总后勤部|中国人民解放军总后勤部]]部长、[[全国政协|全国政协]]副主席。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 新华网 | title = 洪学智同志生平 | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/mil/2006-11/27/content_5396261.htm | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2013-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130912203237/http://news.xinhuanet.com/mil/2006-11/27/content_5396261.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*[[曾绍山|曾绍山]]，[[中国人民解放军中将|中国人民解放军中将]]，曾任辽宁省委第一书记、省革委会主任。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 中国人民解放军开国将帅名录 曾绍山 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587853.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200715130247/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587853.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*[[陈先瑞|陈先瑞]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 中国人民解放军开国将帅名录 陈先瑞 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587583.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200716140655/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587583.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[林维先|林维先]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 中国人民解放军开国将帅名录 林维先 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587611.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200716140701/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587611.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[徐立清|徐立清]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 中国人民解放军开国将帅名录 徐立清 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587745.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200716140828/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587745.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[张贤约|张贤约]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 中国人民解放军开国将帅名录 张贤约 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587507.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200715124020/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/126778/130393/7587507.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[张祖谅|张祖谅]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 党史百科 张祖谅 | url = http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/165618/166491/167908/9975067.html | author =  | date =  | accessdate = 2010-07-04 | archive-date = 2019-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190514211719/http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/165618/166491/167908/9975067.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，中国人民解放军中将。

